\par }{\insrsid13980363 \tab To examine this question it is helpful to begin by generalizing the concept of a machine, which we may define as any technologic device or process intended to achieve some desired result through the expenditure of energy.}{
\insrsid8589476  This generalized machine, depicted in Figure 1, consists of a box in which a certain quantity of delivered fuel energy E}{\sub\insrsid14239721 f}{\super\insrsid8589476  }{\insrsid8589476  is converted into "work"}{\insrsid16527320  W}{
